$interpreted: Surprised Lizard: I can't believe these slaves are still alive!
Suspicious Lizard: Hey! Is this a scam or something...?
Intellectual Lizard: No, they're really fighting! That younger slave is amazing!
Elio: They work really well together...
Sophie: Yeah, with one in the front and one in the back, protecting each other. Works great~
Sanchez: *wheez*...*wheez*... the great Sanchez is tired...
Rune: Sanchez...is a cool guy.
Sanchez: ...hmph.
Sanchez: Quit babbling and get to fighting. Sanchez has got your back!
Rune: Yes!
Devious: ...No way these two rascals...
Colosseum Prison Guard: High Priest! Our warriors have all been defeated! What do we do?
Devious: ...*tisk tisk*...
Devious: Be grateful. Only the strongest challengers have the right to be sacrificed in the Colosseum. Hssssss~
Devious: The two challengers have performed well. I give you my praises! Therefore, in order to prove that our devotion to the Snake Gods does not stop here...
Devious: Bring more. They are no match for the test I have prepared.
Sanchez: More! That's against the rules! We've already won!
Sophie: Test? What test!?
Elio: ...Whatever it is, I don't have a good feeling about this...
Rune: ——BRING IT!
Sophie: WAHHHH!!!!! They destroyed that giant scorpion!
Elio: Sophie?
Sophie: Don't just stare, help us shout!
Sophie: Stand up!
Elio: Huh? What?
Sophie: Ask me later, shout!!
Sophie: Amazing! It must be protection from the Snake God!
Elio: ...Uh, okay...
Elio: Won...they've won!! They beat all their opponents!
Sophie: Too quiet! You've got to shout even louder!!
Elio: ...Do I have to!?
Sophie: There's no other way.
Sophie: We've got to make everyone think they've won~
Elio: ...I see! No wonder you're a Ringmaster. You know how to grab an opportunity when you see one!
Sophie: I...I...I'm just okay, I think~
Elio: Okay, let me have a go.
Elio: Fi...Finally——
Sophie: Too shrill, Elio! More natural!
Elio: *cough*...Finally——warriors that are worthy of surviving to the very end!!
Surprised Lizard: They won! They really won!!
Intellectual Lizard: Wow! What a show! Give them a round of applause!
Sanchez: Hu...he...ha...haha! We're...alive!!
Rune: ...We...won...?
Diana: Congratulations, you two.
Sanchez: Your Majesty, the Queen...
Diana: You have achieved a glorious victory in this Colosseum.
Lazer: Your bravery and ferocity have proved your innocence.
Devious: ...and the respect of the Snake God and Goddess.
Diana: With the power granted to me as Queen, I hereby pardon your crimes and remove your identity as slaves.
Diana: ——From here on out, you are free!
Lazer: An exciting atmosphere and a successful event. Congratulations, Your Highness.
Lazer: ...No blood was spilled and everyone is still happy.
Devious: You...
Sophie: What's that noise? An explosion!?
Elio: Is that...a Monster? How is that possible!?
Clergy Member: Don't run away! Stand still!
Clergy Member: What are you staring at!? Help me!
Uzziah: You may not...come here!
Colosseum Prison Guard: Don't...don't eat me!!
Sophie: That man...how'd they get into the Colosseum? Did he use Rune magic?
Elio: No. There's no currently known Rune that can call forth Monsters...!
Devious: The Snake God's sacred Martyrs' Colosseum, disrupted by you! What are you waiting for? Grab these intruders at once!
Lazer: Surrounded!
Uzziah: Sorry, but I can't let them catch me...
Uzziah: ...no matter whatever it takes!
Surprised Lizard: They're coming...wahhhhh!!!!
Frightened Lizard: Run, run!!!!
Diana: It's dangerous. Everybody be careful...
Lazer: Your Majesty, get behind me!
Diana: I'm fine. Go save the others!
Lazer: You know I can't do that, child. I am here to protect you.
Diana: ...Protect the citizens!
Sophie: Rune! Are you okay?
Rune: ...Sophie.
Elio: Be careful, they're coming!
Sophie: We're good for now. Rune, get out of here while you still can!
